#: ../../M/munchkin.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from the squeaky-voiced little people in L. Frank Baum's *The Wizard of "
"Oz*\\] A teenage-or-younger micro enthusiast hacking BASIC or something else"
" equally constricted. A term of mild derision — munchkins are annoying but "
"some grow up to be hackers after passing through a :ref:`larval-stage`\\. "
"The term :ref:`urchin` is also used. See also :ref:`wannabee`\\, "
":ref:`bitty-box`\\."
msgstr ""
"[L. Frank Baumの\\ *The Wizard of Oz*\\ "
"のかん高い声の小さな人々から]BASICか、同じくらい制約された何かをハックするティーンエイジ以下のマイコン愛好家。軽い嘲りの語——munchkinは煩わしいが、一部は\\"
" :ref:`larval-stage`\\ を経てハッカーに成長する。\\ :ref:`urchin`\\ という語も使われる。\\ "
":ref:`wannabee`\\ 、\\ :ref:`bitty-box`\\ も参照。"
